  m_Name: ScenarioData-2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: 'End of Training

    Several months have passed since you joined
    Aterra Media & Data Control.

    What once felt unfamiliar has become part of
    your daily routine. Intercepting harmful data now comes naturally, and you''ve
    grown comfortable with your workstation.


    Today marks the end of your training
    period.

    Even after months of working here, Aterra remains a mystery. Every
    department operates independently, employees only know their own responsibilities,
    and no one seems to talk about what happens beyond their division.


    This
    morning, Supervisor Alice told you that Boss Jackson wanted to speak with you
    before your shift.

    She didn''t say why.

    You''re a little nervous...
    but also curious.'
  CompanyHeirarchySprites: []
